Title: Den sommeren jeg fylte 15
Writer: Knut Andersen, Knut Faldbakken (novel), Knut Faldbakken (screenplay)
Actors: Steffen Rothschild, Anne-Lise Tangstad, Kaare Kroppan, Grethe Ryen
Plot: Peter is telling his story about a special summer, when he was invited over to summer holiday from bickering parents, to his aunt and uncle in the country. He's been there before, but this summer was quite one to remember.
